        {
            "title": "聯儲會官員抨擊哈塞特言論 稱其破壞央行獨立性",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 明尼阿波利斯聯儲行長尼爾·<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-ylk=\"slk:卡什卡利;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/卡什卡利\">卡什卡利</a>表示，國家經濟委員會主任<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-ylk=\"slk:凱文·哈塞特;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/凱文·哈塞特\">凱文·哈塞特</a>近期對於紐約聯儲關稅研究的批評言論破壞了央行獨立性。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">「這只是試圖損害聯儲會獨立性的又一步，」卡什卡利周四在北達科他州法戈的一場活動中談及哈塞特言論時表示，「過去的一年裡，我們已經看到多次損害聯儲會獨立性的嘗試。」</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"視頻：明尼阿波利斯聯邦儲備銀行行長尼爾·卡什卡利批評國家經濟委員會主任凱文·哈塞特對紐約聯儲會關稅研究的評論。來源： 彭博\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"540\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/FrKxsMfZprAE_PJAUKcz9Q--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0MA--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/662101ea5b09e8d847c61bc125cc5480\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">視頻：明尼阿波利斯聯邦儲備銀行行長尼爾·卡什卡利批評國家經濟委員會主任凱文·哈塞特對紐約聯儲會關稅研究的評論。來源： 彭博</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">紐約聯儲經濟學家研究發現川普加徵關稅的大部分由美國企業承擔，哈塞特認為這個研究「令人難堪」，相關人員應受到「處分」。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-c072724f-0c53-3a36-a113-39f20480d9c8-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">卡什卡利表示，「我們竭儘全力根據數據和分析對經濟做出最佳評估」。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">「抱緊桅桿」</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">卡什卡利還指出，目前司法部對聯儲會大樓翻修工程的調查是川普政府施壓的證據。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">在談到聯儲會實現價格穩定和充分就業的雙重使命時，卡什卡利說，「噪音越大，我們就越會‘抱緊桅桿’，堅守我們的使命」。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">在利率問題上，卡什卡利表示，聯儲會的基準利率目前可能接近「中性」水平。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Kashkari Rips Hassett Criticism of NY Fed Tariff Analysis (2)</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">--聯合報導 Matt Shirley.</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E8%81%AF%E5%84%B2%E6%9C%83%E5%AE%98%E5%93%A1%E6%8A%A8%E6%93%8A%E5%93%88%E5%A1%9E%E7%89%B9%E8%A8%80%E8%AB%96-%E7%A8%B1%E5%85%B6%E7%A0%B4%E5%A3%9E%E5%A4%AE%E8%A1%8C%E7%8D%A8%E7%AB%8B%E6%80%A7-164013480.html",
