        },
        {
            "title": "印度力爭AI樞紐地位 總理莫迪強調開放與共享",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 印度總理莫迪將印度定位為可負擔且可規模化的<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-ylk=\"slk:人工智能;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/人工智能\">人工智能</a>樞紐，表示在這個南亞國家開發的創新成果可在全球推廣應用。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">莫迪在新德里舉行的一場人工智能峰會上發表主旨演講時表示：「在印度設計和開發，為世界服務，為人類服務。」</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">這場被稱為開發中國家舉辦的最大規模人工智能會議為莫迪提供了一個平台，彰顯印度在這一主要由美國和中國主導的競賽中的角色。印度政府藉此展示該國龐大、精通技術的民眾基礎與深厚的工程人才儲備，以此證明其能夠提供全球科技巨頭塑造的人工智能模型的替代方案。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-5d153557-1a88-3c3b-bafe-e48df325e0c6-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">「有些國家和企業認為人工智能是一種戰略資產。但印度認為，只有共享並開放代碼，人工智能才能造福世界，」莫迪說，強調普及人工智能的必要性。「我們有人才、能源供給能力，也有清晰的政策方向。」</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">來自法國和巴西在內的十多位國家領導人本周出席此次峰會，OpenAI、Alphabet Inc.和Anthropic PBC等人工智能巨頭的高管也到場參會。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">推薦閱讀：印度首富承諾最高投資1100億美元建AI基礎設施 多巨頭相繼加碼押注</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Modi Touts India as Hub for Affordable AI at New Delhi Summit</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">--聯合報導 Dan Strumpf.</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%8D%B0%E5%BA%A6%E5%8A%9B%E7%88%ADai%E6%A8%9E%E7%B4%90%E5%9C%B0%E4%BD%8D-%E7%B8%BD%E7%90%86%E8%8E%AB%E8%BF%AA%E5%BC%B7%E8%AA%BF%E9%96%8B%E6%94%BE%E8%88%87%E5%85%B1%E4%BA%AB-123525433.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-02-19 21:14:40",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "亞馬遜現時是否值得買入？",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"408\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/PiWDk69Vw_8lugd9Qr_2KA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MA--/https://media.zenfs.com/ca/hk_moneyclub_713/ad03a52609a0324e1bdbfc37a285d40c\" width=\"612\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">電商及雲運算巨頭<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-ylk=\"slk:亞馬遜;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/亞馬遜\">亞馬遜</a>（AMZN）股價在年初表現強勁後，近日因公布2025年第四季度及全年業績而急挫，引發市場關注：現時應否乘機「撈底」，抑或該股已淪為「接飛刀」？</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">過去3年，亞馬遜大幅加快資本開支步伐；AI需求急速上升，令公司需要在整條基建價值鏈加大投資，包括興建數據中心、自行設計專用晶片，並配合向Nvidia採購GPU。華爾街原本預期管理層今年資本開支指引約1500億美元，實際公佈的約2000億美元計劃令市場大跌眼鏡，引發估值壓縮。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-27300d9a-822d-3a90-8688-3397316dff30-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"547\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/54OdDzkvPAzUCXBpaRwfjw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU4Mw--/https://media.zenfs.com/ca/hk_moneyclub_713/a91784c6065ba4f2cd4d347f033ef5e0\" width=\"900\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">投資者憂慮之處，在於基建投資與自由現金流呈明顯反向關係；不過，若從亞馬遜WebServices（AWS）收入及營運利潤增長角度出發，情況便不一樣。過去一年AWS收入及利潤率均持續提升，為公司提供資本推動多個AI項目，包括自建數據中心及自家晶片，以及對Anthropic的策略性投資，實際上是在推動其AI業務垂直整合，長遠有助降低成本及提升盈利增長。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"548\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/Job6ky1qwi3y0JmE3Ajp0A--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU4Nw--/https://media.zenfs.com/ca/hk_moneyclub_713/db5e81e5464f14836b17a07adf98157e\" width=\"896\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">目前亞馬遜的預測市盈率接近整個AI熱潮以來的最低水平，在AWS增長重新加速、利潤率穩健的背景下，現價看來具吸引力。雖然市場對執行風險有所擔憂，但亞馬遜至今在策略執行上表現不俗，筆者認為近期股價回調屬過度反應，對長線投資者而言，亞馬遜不僅是「可以買」，更是值得「買入並長期持有」的優質標的。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">作者：Adam Spatacco, The Fool</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文刊登於 HKMoneyClub</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">更多你或感興趣內容：</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:重溫「股壇長毛」David Webb的8大長線致勝法則;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.hkmoneyclub.com/2026/01/14/%e9%87%8d%e6%ba%ab%e3%80%8c%e8%82%a1%e5%a3%87%e9%95%b7%e6%af%9b%e3%80%8ddavid-webb%e7%9a%848%e5%a4%a7%e9%95%b7%e7%b7%9a%e8%87%b4%e5%8b%9d%e6%b3%95%e5%89%87/\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">重溫「股壇長毛」David Webb的8大長線致勝法則</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:白銀2025年飆升144% 但歷史暗示2026年或大跌;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.hkmoneyclub.com/2026/01/28/%e7%99%bd%e9%8a%802025%e5%b9%b4%e9%a3%86%e5%8d%87144-%e4%bd%86%e6%ad%b7%e5%8f%b2%e6%9a%97%e7%a4%ba2026%e5%b9%b4%e6%88%96%e5%a4%a7%e8%b7%8c/\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">白銀2025年飆升144% 但歷史暗示2026年或大跌</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:擔心AI泡沫爆破？這3種較穩陣的選擇可為投資組合提供防護;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.hkmoneyclub.com/2026/01/30/%e6%93%94%e5%bf%83ai%e6%b3%a1%e6%b2%ab%e7%88%86%e7%a0%b4%ef%bc%9f%e9%80%993%e7%a8%ae%e8%bc%83%e7%a9%a9%e9%99%a3%e7%9a%84%e9%81%b8%e6%93%87%e5%8f%af%e7%82%ba%e6%8a%95%e8%b3%87%e7%b5%84%e5%90%88/\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">擔心AI泡沫爆破？這3種較穩陣的選擇可為投資組合提供防護</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">睇完新聞，記得追蹤hkmoneyclub以下平台，接收更多分析評論！</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">YouTube：hkmoneyclub (https://www.youtube.com/@hkmoneyclub)</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">本文所提供的信息僅供一般參考之用，並不構成任何個人化的投資勸誘或建議。作者沒持有以上提及的股票。 <span>HK MoneyClub</span> (www.hkmoneyclub.com)</p></div>",
