        {
            "title": "高盛稱跑贏基準的大型股主動型共同基金比例已創2007年以來最高",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"Bloomberg\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"440\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/r6Bu3rpsGsrqnxmdibO_xQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTQ0MA--/https://media.zenfs.com/no/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/3f2c345d97c259e3b04e5a11186838f2\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">Bloomberg</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 高盛策略師指出，隨著股市漲勢從科技巨頭向其他領域擴散，今年迄今跑贏基準的大型股主動型共同基金比例已創2007年以來最高。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">包括Ryan Hammond在內的團隊在報告中指出，其中57%的基金今年迄今跑贏基準。這一比例遠高於2007年以來的37%平均水平，Hammond認為部分原因在於巨型科技股回報疲軟。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Hammond表示，「投資者今年正消化各種宏觀和微觀層面的交叉影響，包括周期性加速的前景，以及人工智能顛覆帶來的所謂‘贏家’和‘輸家’。這些主題促使股市回報範圍擴大，不再局限於過去幾年推動指數上漲的少數幾只股票。」</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-66ffd4da-159c-3f05-aab6-988273ad4311-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\" \" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"440\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/0evlqR.aDmurfNaSxE7ERA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTQ0MA--/https://media.zenfs.com/no/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/ffc66a049ff89a246c927f6763beeffc\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\"> </figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">今年科技七巨頭表現平平，為傳統上採用主動管理策略的共同基金創造了機遇。高盛策略師指出，這些基金普遍降低軟件板塊配置的舉措，使其收益免受近期市場動盪的衝擊。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">但策略師強調，基金選擇依然關鍵。儘管65%的大盤核心股基金和60%的大盤成長股基金跑贏，但價值股基金的這一比例降至42%。策略師同時指出從主動型基金持續向被動型基金轉移的趨勢，不過他們也注意到，今年迄今美國股票主動型ETF獲得310億美元資金流入是個例外。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">根據該報告，共同基金目前對金融和工業板塊的超配程度最高，而對信息技術板塊的低配程度最為明顯。現金持倉比例已降至1.1%，為有記錄以來的最低水平。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Goldman Says Most Large-Cap Stock Pickers Beat Market Since 2007</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">--聯合報導 Michael Msika.</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
